message: Hello Bob, I'm offering you a valuable product for $1,300,000. I believe this price reflects its significant worth.
Thank you for your offer, Alice. I appreciate the value of the product, but I can only commit to a maximum of $1,200,000. I hope we can come to an agreement.
Bob, I understand your position, but I believe the product's value warrants a higher price. Would you consider $1,275,000?
I see that you're standing firm on your valuation, Alice. I'm willing to go up to $1,250,000 for the product. I hope this aligns better with your expectations.
